=========================
THE HISTORY OF PSYCHOBALL
=========================

*************************************************
(19/08/2013) Version 1.0.0    -  PsyChO Unchained
*************************************************
-RELEASE OF PSYCHO

-New Adventure Mode!
	-FOUR levels!
	-Levels scripted and packed with glorious PsyChOMadness!
	-FOUR AWESOME BOSSES!
	-Over 8 brand-new or modified enemies (9 enemies to be exact)!
-Added Practice mode
	-Use it to master the adventure mode and pass those difficult patterns
	-Unlock more levels by reaching them on adventure mode
-Added Death explosions
	-Different equations that makes your death awesome
-Added original soundtrack!
	-New menu song "Flying Carrots 2"
	-New survival and adventure song "Limitless"
-Added basic controller support!
	-You can, in game, move Psycho and shoot with the analog sticks
	-Any other button triggers Ultrablast
	-However you can't move around the menu or pause...
-Added SplashScreen for Marvellous Soft
-Added new death messages
-Changes on the balance of the game
-Some minors bugs fixed
-Removed previosuly soundtrack
-Removed menu random messages
*************************************************
(16/06/2013) Version 0.9.1    -  Long way to go
*************************************************

-Changes on Changelog
-Changes on suPerbALLs
	- They are spawned every 30 seconds
	- For every 90 seconds on survivor mode, their on-screen limit increases by 1

*************************************************
(16/06/2013) Version 0.9.0    -  PsyChO Reborn
*************************************************

-Change on the script
	-More "understandable" code!
	-Support for images
-Added a menu
	-Buttons
	-Transition between screens
	-New screen for Controls
	-Regular mode is now Survivor
	-From pause or death screen you can go back to menu
	-New menu song "The Synergy vs N.V.R. - Re-Control"
-Added random menu messages
-Added random pause messages
-Added new death messages
	-Added a very rare death message
-Added new type of enemy: suPerbALLs
-Added new easter-eggs
	-Added David Robert Jones mode
	-Added Italian mode
	-Added Richard mode
	-Added Detective mode
	-Added TILT mode
	-Added DK mode
	-Added The Code
-New file that saves your configurations
	-Saves your last sound control setting when the game is closed
-Changes on how files are created/read
-You can reset your stats in the main menu
-You can only use easter-eggs and devmode on survivor for now 
-Major changes on difficulty of Survivor mode
-Changes on text placement
	-New font for some texts
-Changes on focus
	-While on survivor mode you can't lose focus
	-While paused or anywhere else you can
-Changes on how score works
	-It counts how many points you've made
	-You no longer dies if you score hits 0
	-Saves your highscore
-Changes on Ultrablast
	-Limited times you can use it
	-You get more if you get more points
	-You get more if you survive more time (survivor mode)
	-Instead of a ring, PsyChObALL will grow when using Ultrablast
-Changes on color settings
	-Changes on "LSD worn out" effect
	-Changes on color of "bullets"
-Fixed some sound control bugs
	-Muting when the song is weither fading in or fading out

*************************************************
(11/05/2013) Version 0.8.0    -   UltraUpdate
*************************************************

-Major change on the script
	-"Cleaner" code
	-More annotations
-Added "Ultrablast Charge"
-Added sound controller
	-You can press 'm' to mute the game
	-You can press ',' or '.' to decrease or increase the volume
	-Added images representing current sound level
-Added the logo
-Added slow-motion effect on death
-Added version checker
-Added devmode
-Added hidden easter-egg: "ghost mode"
	-Lets you know if there is a newer version available at the site
	-Timeouts if it doesn't get any info from the site after a set time
-You can't leave the screen anymore
-Explosion particles have the colour of their "origin"
-Changes on text placement
-More death messages
	-Getting "LSD worn out" effect is more difficult
	-Leaving "LSD worn out" effect is more common
-Changed 10x multiplier colour effect

*************************************************
(25/04/2013) Version 0.7.9   -  Everyday Patch
*************************************************

-Fixed generic sound bugs
-Added instructions to "Ultrablast"
-Some new death messages
-Tweaks on multiplier effects on score
    -Multiplier on losing points slightly reduced
    -Multiplier on wining points slightly increased

*************************************************
(17/04/2013) Version 0.7.8  - The Rise of PsyChO
*************************************************

-First release of PsyChObALL!

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
A GAME BY MARVELLOUS SOFT/USPGAMEDEV
